high_descs: Head straight for the door, turn right towards the shelves, turn right towards the long table.
Pick up the green sponge on the table.
Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Place the sponge in the sink, wash it, and take it back out.
Turn left towards the stove and then turn left towards the wooden shelves.
Place the sponge on the plate on the shelves.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed sponge on the plate on the shelves.

high_descs: Walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk to the far side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the sponge off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the sponge in the sink then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean sponge.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then hang a left and walk over to the wooden shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the clean sponge on the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit in front of the grey plate.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the shelf of a wooden shelving unit.

high_descs: Move towards the door, then turn right and move towards the brown shelves in the corner of the room, the turn right and face the kitchen island.
Pick up the green sponge between the ladle and the spatula from the kitchen island.
Turn left and move towards the white range then turn right and move to the sink between the dishwasher and the refrigerator.
Place the sponge in the sink to the right of the glass, immerse it in water, let the water drain, and then pick up the clean sponge.
Turn left and move towards the green bin at the end of the kitchen counter and in front of the window, then turn left and move to the brown shelves in the corner.
Place the sponge on the plate on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean sponge on a plate on a shelf.
